,"msg":"據我估計，會員應該係香港人比較多(求fact check)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係所有幹事都係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9f6a24be9cb07eb85b7eaa0f4e9773d4c19df7","tid":1307105,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc7801d117e38389941a303dcf4c32a63350f91e","tid":1307105,"uid":30283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c3a65c2afde836df66d179716640fd04af28fe84","tid":1307105,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"會員大陸人定香港人多？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"據我估計，會員應該係香港人比較多(求fact check)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係所有幹事都係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e133903024d26b9a9646c60ec2e1bc459fabbfd","tid":1307105,"uid":94968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4f723c961112c3d9929cca28c0bcfca0f8c8a1e2","tid":1307105,"uid":30283,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"【即時新聞】研究生會指控學生會：「嚴重干涉了我會內務」<br />\n<br />\n香港大學研究生會（研究生會）今（7月11日）早向會員發電郵，提及香港大學學生會（學生會）於7月10日發電郵，替兩名研究生會會員發佈早前嘗試於週年會員大會所提出的議案。研究生會稱該封由學生會所發出的電郵為「學生會官郵發起的動議」，變相形容學生會於研究生會週年會員大會上提出動議，更指責學生會的舉動「嚴重干涉了我會內務」。但實情是研究生會會員嘗試提出動議，並使用了學生會提供的電郵服務向同學發佈消息，而不是由學生會提出動議。<br />\n<br />\n本台訪問了學生會署理行政秘書馮卓傑，馮表示：「學生會在事件中完全沒有表達任何立場，亦未有嘗試干涉研究生會內務；發電郵一事中，本人亦只是根據學生會內務守則讓同學使用學生會提供的服務。」<br />\n<br />\n學生會內務守則中列明：「會員、大學各委員會的學生代表，以及由香港大學學生成立及管理但非學生會組織亦可使用此服務，次數限每學期一次，並須經行政秘書批准。」由於在研究生會週年會員大會提案的研究生會會員同為學生會基本會員，因此該名同學是符合使用學生會電郵服務的資格。<br />\n<br />\n研究生會今早的電郵除了指控學生會干涉研究生會內務外，研究生會亦稱會員於周年會員大會上提案是「強行塞入議案」，所以拒絕於大會上對任何由會員提交的動議作討論。但有會員認為此乃橫蠻無理之舉，因為周年會員大會應允許所有會員參與會議，當中包括投票或提出動議；若果只有幹事會可以提出動議，而會員提出則被指為「強行塞入」的說法毫無道理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/233771423482007/posts/1103748429817631?s=1085545881&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F233771423482007%2Fposts%2F1103748429817631%3Fs%3D1085545881%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjl7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=7999483e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/233771423482007/posts/1103748429817631?s=1085545881&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n腔調同口交部一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fea9b40a6f2770b157902ed274144287baa40d","tid":1307105,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f187a515b4955a81fed82c0bfa547d0bc565a1","tid":1307105,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33d485719a421e9fcd6cb09b4b554c5641b33be5","tid":1307105,"uid":18845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f723c961112c3d9929cca28c0bcfca0f8c8a1e2","tid":1307105,"uid":30283,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"【即時新聞】研究生會指控學生會：「嚴重干涉